def is_suitable_cup(cup: item):
    # Function to check if the item is a suitable cup or glass
    symbol suitable_cup = is_cup(cup) and grabbable(cup)

            bind cup: item where:
                is_suitable_cup(cup)
            achieve close_char(char, cup)
        else:
